Package: sapthesisdown
Title: An R Markdown version of the Sapthesis template using thesisdown and bookdown packages
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Tullia", "Padellini", email = "tullia.padellini@uniroma1.it", role = "cre"),
    person("Francesco", "Biccari", email = "biccari@gmail.com", role = "aut"))
Description: This is an adaptation of the thesisdown package to the sapthesis LaTeX template. 
    It can be used to write Bachelor, Master, PhD and specialization theses following the 
    guidelines of Sapienza University of Rome.
Maintainer: Tullia Padellini <tullia.padellini@uniroma1.it>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0),
    devtools,
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    bookdown,
    knitr
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
SystemRequirements: pandoc (>= 1.18) - http://pandoc.org
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
